  "detailed_description": "The Lost Prince is a story-based package game developed with the motif of the fairy tale ‘The Little Prince’.<br />\r\nIt is a visual novel-based complex genre in which the story begins with the assumption that the prince died from a snakebite.<br />\r\nThrough optional branching through dialogue, you can see multiple endings related to the three heroines.<br />\r\nYou can enjoy simple mini-games during the training process, as well as turn-based battles between games.",
  "about_the_game": "The Lost Prince is a story-based package game developed with the motif of the fairy tale ‘The Little Prince’.<br />\r\nIt is a visual novel-based complex genre in which the story begins with the assumption that the prince died from a snakebite.<br />\r\nThrough optional branching through dialogue, you can see multiple endings related to the three heroines.<br />\r\nYou can enjoy simple mini-games during the training process, as well as turn-based battles between games.",
